<item>
            <title>[LU-17171] sanity-quota 41 may fail on zfs backend</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17171</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The block size is 4k on zfs backend, the block used will be multiple of 4k. In sanity-quota 41, &apos;df&apos; returns project quota value, and the result should match the result of &apos;lfs quota&apos;, but quota result is shown in 1k, if the real blocks used is not multiple of 4k, the results will mismatch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
